%F A125175 T(n,k) = binomial(n+1,k) if n+k even. T(n,k) = binomial(n-1,k)*(n+k)/(n-k) if n+k odd. - _R. J. Mathar_, Sep 08 2013
%e A125175 First few rows of the triangle are:
%e A125175   1;
